<div class="dlp">
    <h2>Scientific Working Group</h2>
    <section class="main">

        <p>As part of PATRIC, we have established a Scientific Working Group (SWG) comprised of members with deep
            expertise in a broad range of domains of relevance to PATRIC. The SWG provides advice about the management
            and performance of the resource, and about the needs of the scientific community in relation to the
            resource.</p>

